entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You defended the Stronghold from Sulfur Lake Pirates.
entries.journal_entry_description: Meet with the envoy from Tatooine.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Find the Landing Clearance Control Panel in front of the Stronghold.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Grant the envoy shuttle permission to land in front of the Stronghold.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Authorization to land received. See you on the ground. Heh ha ha.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Great the envoy and escort them to the Stronghold lobby to meet Nym.
entries.task04_start_message: Something doesn't seem right about the shuttle.
entries.task04_utterance_wave_1: Nym will pay for all he has done to the Sulfur Lake Pirates! Kill everyone!!!
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Speak with Nym in the Stronghold.
entries.task07_comm_message_text: We've scanned the shuttle. I have a feeling something is up. Get ready to defend yourself! I'm on my way!
